ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Highly recommended. It will not only teach you about database technologies but also some considerations and trade-offs in designing such a complicated system.But be prepared to read a lot of research papers. In addition, you'd better have already learned CS437/537 or the equivalent before taking this course.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It helps me to understand the state-of-the-art database/data store technologies, which may be quite helpful in my future career.
I've directly become involved in some research as a result of this course.
